title: The Irate Gamer Volume 1 DVD Full

This torrent is for the first volume of \"The Irate Gamer\" straight from the official DVD. 

The Irate Gamer is the new critically acclaimed video review show. Chris Bores masterfully reviews classic video games while including skits, cut away gags, special effects and more while becoming irate in the process. This DVD includes the first 11 episodes all re-mastered specially for this release, and includes memorable moments featuring classic games.
